hcc_text: Cross Bx Service Road South is in the middle third in the Bronx for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile.
info: At Cross Bx Service Road South at Cross Bx Exwy Nb Exit 5 B and Powell Avenue, there were 14 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
